# 005. Use of 'z' and international spelling

Date: 2022-07-14

## Status

Accepted

## Context

Unified naming convention for word with British & International spelling: organization/organisation. 

## Decision

Use international version of spelling the word: organization.

## Consequences

Consistent codebase less prone to errors.

